leetcode https://leetcode.com/problems/assign-cookies/

Kontha mandi pillalu (children) unnaru.

Prathi pilladiki oka greed factor untundi.

Greed factor ante aa pilladu happy avvadaniki minimum entha size cookie kavalo adi.

Cookies kuda different sizes untayi.

Rules:
Oka child ki okka cookie matrame ivvali.
Oka cookie ni okka child ki matrame ivvali.
Cookie size >= child greed factor ayithe aa child happy.

Mana goal enti?

👉 Maximum number of children ni happy cheyyali.
Example 1
g = [1,2,3]

s = [1,1]

g = children greed factors

Child1 ki 1 size cookie saripothundi

Child2 ki 2 size cookie kavali

Child3 ki 3 size cookie kavali

Cookies:

1,1

Ippudu

Cookie 1 → Child1 ✅

Inko cookie 1

Cookie 1 → Child2 ❌

Endhukante Child2 ki minimum 2 kavali.

Child3 ki kuda 3 kavali.

Kabatti answer:

1 child happy
